## Development

This project uses [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) for dependency management.

```bash
# Clone and install
{%- if spec.github is defined -%}
git clone https://github.com/{{ spec.github.org | default("OWNER") }}/{{ spec.github.repo | default(spec.name) }}.git
{%- else -%}
git clone https://github.com/OWNER/{{ spec.name }}.git
{%- endif %}
cd {{ spec.name }}
uv sync

# Run tests
uv run pytest

# Lint and format
uv run ruff check .
uv run ruff format .

# Type check
uv run mypy {{ spec.structure.src_dir | default("src") }}/
```
